{"tid":757768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保護核技術】德國傳禁機械公司Leifeld售予中國投資者","createTime":"2018-07-27T06:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T00:18:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17d736400399aabdd9f69d8810a35f1e0954d1e0","tid":757768,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:15:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180727&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58492251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180727%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58492251&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=2bf98249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180727%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58492251&h=664068db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180727&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58492251</a><br />\n【保護核技術】德國傳禁機械公司Leifeld售予中國投資者<br />\n<br />\n中國資金重重受困，繼美眾議院通過限制中國在美投資法案，德國亦擬阻止一公司售予中國投資者，若成事將會是德國首次以國家安全為由禁止中方資金投資。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述德國官員消息，下週三的內閣會議，將正式宣布禁止德國機械工具公司Leifeld Metal Spinning AG售予中國投資者，稱政府深入調查後，認為交易將對公眾秩序及安全構成風險，希望該公司的火箭及核技術繼續掌握在德國手中。<br />\n<br />\n德國經濟部門無有透露交易詳情，中國投資者身份及投資金額等細節未明。"},{"pid":"aaf24d07683f0243c4061279cd031e18401d242c","tid":757768,"uid":165377,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"突然諗起中國以前收購IBM PC部門全國上下J到出晒血<br />\n果陣仲細以為真係IBM都要跪低<br />\n最尾先知人地一早將成個business model轉型賣D二手貨比你執人地口水尾仲咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a281fd706a3ba03d8be31509610b73e3dfe5c6b","tid":757768,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又贏"},{"pid":"e2af5c0009f25ece962c8961ea5da52ce6bd2dc9","tid":75